request.description:
sport_type => must be in ['basketball','handball']
"match_id" => must be integer and in matches table
currently there are (1,2,3) only matches

example 
<=============================================>
{
    "sport_type":"basketball",
    "match_id":2
}
<=============================================>
{
    "sport_type":"handball",
    "match_id":3
}
<=============================================>
{
    "sport_type":"handball",
    "match_id":1
}
